  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "HINet HINet explores the impact of Instance Normalization on low-level vision tasks by introducing the Half Instance Normalization Block (HIN Block), designed to boost image restoration network performance (Chen et al. 2021).",
    "This innovation is key to HINet, a robust multi-stage network that incorporates two U-Net-based subnetworks.",
    "These subnetworks are seamlessly integrated using a Cross-stage Feature Fusion (CSFF) module and a Supervised Attention Module, ensuring effective feature integration.",
    "Each subnetwork consists of a series of HIN Blocks and Res Blocks, with the HIN Block applying instance normalization to only half of the feature map, leaving the rest unchanged.",
    "This distinctive approach enables HINet to achieve superior results across various image restoration tasks, marking a significant advancement in the field."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "HINet HINet explores the impact of Instance Normalization on low-level vision tasks by introducing the Half Instance Normalization Block (HIN Block), designed to boost image restoration network performance (Chen et al. 2021)."
